name: Fauna Flowers 12 - Capivara Flower
description:
A furry funny friendly flower. (I dare you to say that rapidly three times in a row). If you have found one of it, you have found a bunch of it, always by the water. Sometimes on soil, sometimes in the water. Conveys calm and tranquility to the garden. Very sociable and loved by all the harmonic buddies.

Fauna Flowers is a collection made of animals mixed with plants in a new kind of magical possibilities. Discover this world where flowers can be a magnificent diversity of beautiful and unique creatures.
